Text: This downloaded and installed as "License: Team Viewer Server Enterprise (1 channel)." What exactly does this mean?
After successful installation of this torrent Team Viewer will offer to update to version 6.0.11117. If you do it will  revert to the free version.
in the crack folder there are three files which one is the exe file,,,please explain more thanx

@shakuur, You need to copy all the 3 .exe files from the crack folder over to the C:\Program Files\TeamViewer\Version6 and overwrite when asked.

And if running win 7 and your not able to overwrite the exe files, then you will need to stop the Teamviewer 6 Service, by going to start -> in the search type Services -> and then you should see services, click it -> then the services window should open -> search for TeamViewer 6, right click it and click Stop then  you should be able to copy the 3 .exe files -> after your done copying, start the TeamViewer 6 service again. Enjoy!!!
